{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sendBadges:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSInteger","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSInteger"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"badge"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The current application badge number (0 to clear badge)."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"badge"}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Reports the current badge count to Pushwoosh for analytics and to enable"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"badge-based segmentation. This is useful for:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Analytics"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Track user engagement through unread counts"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Segmentation"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Target users with high\/low badge counts","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Badge management"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Allow server-side badge manipulation"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Call this method whenever you update the app badge to keep Pushwoosh in sync."}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Example","text":"Example","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sync badge with Pushwoosh when updating unread counts:"}]},{"code":["class NotificationBadgeManager {","","    private(set) var unreadCount: Int = 0 {","        didSet {","            updateBadge()","        }","    }","","    func markAsRead(_ notificationIds: [String]) {","        unreadCount = max(0, unreadCount - notificationIds.count)","    }","","    func handleNewNotification() {","        unreadCount += 1","    }","","    func clearAll() {","        unreadCount = 0","    }","","    private func updateBadge() {","        \/\/ Update system badge","        if #available(iOS 16.0, *) {","            UNUserNotificationCenter.current().setBadgeCount(unreadCount)","        } else {","            UIApplication.shared.applicationIconBadgeNumber = unreadCount","        }","","        \/\/ Sync with Pushwoosh","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(unreadCount)","    }","}","","\/\/ Usage in AppDelegate","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func applicationDidBecomeActive(_ application: UIApplication) {","        \/\/ Sync current badge state when app becomes active","        let currentBadge = application.applicationIconBadgeNumber","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(currentBadge)","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/sendBadges:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/sendbadges:"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Synchronizes the application badge number with Pushwoosh servers."}],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)sendBadges:","symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"sendBadges:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sendBadges:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"sendBadges:"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/sendBadges:":{"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sendBadges:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"sendBadges:","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Synchronizes the application badge number with Pushwoosh servers."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/sendbadges:","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/sendBadges:","title":"sendBadges:"}}}